{#
/**
 * @file
 * _search-icon.html.twig
 *
 * Search form toggle button.
 *
 * Renders a button that toggles the visibility of the collapsible
 * search form region (#CollapseSearch) using Bootstrap's collapse JS.
 *
 * Accessibility:
 * - aria-label="Open search" describes the *action* (opening the form),
 *   not just the concept of search. This is more accurate for screen
 *   reader users than a generic "Search" label, which implies the button
 *   performs a search rather than revealing a form.
 * - aria-expanded is managed automatically by Bootstrap JS when toggled.
 *   It starts as "false" because the search panel is collapsed by default.
 * - aria-controls links this button to the collapsible region it controls.
 * - The SVG uses aria-hidden="true" and focusable="false":
 *     aria-hidden="true"  — removes the SVG from the accessibility tree
 *                           entirely. The button's aria-label provides
 *                           the accessible name, so the SVG is redundant
 *                           to screen readers.
 *     focusable="false"   — prevents IE/legacy Edge from placing focus
 *                           on the SVG element itself, which would create
 *                           a confusing extra tab stop.
 *
 * NOTE: role="img" has been intentionally removed from the SVG.
 *       It directly contradicts aria-hidden="true". When aria-hidden is
 *       set, the element is removed from the accessibility tree, making
 *       any role assignment on it meaningless. Using both together is
 *       invalid and confusing — aria-hidden wins, so role="img" was
 *       doing nothing except adding noise.
 *
 * Styling:
 * - btn-link keeps the button visually minimal (no border/background).
 * - p-0 and text-dark keep it flush and consistently colored.
 * - Replace these classes as needed to match your design system.
 */
#}

<button
        class="search-icon btn btn-link p-0 text-dark"
        type="button"
        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
        data-bs-target="#CollapseSearch"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="CollapseSearch"
        aria-label="{{ 'Open search'|t }}">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
         width="16" height="16"
         fill="currentColor"
         class="bi bi-search"
         viewBox="0 0 16 16"
         aria-hidden="true"
         focusable="false">
        <path d="M11.742 10.344a6.5 6.5 0 1 0-1.397 1.398h-.001q.044.06.098.115l3.85 3.85a1 1 0 0 0 1.415-1.414l-3.85-3.85a1 1 0 0 0-.115-.1zM12 6.5a5.5 5.5 0 1 1-11 0 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 11 0"/>
    </svg>
</button>
